<div class="col-12 about-text py-2 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
    <div class="p-lg-3 pe-lg-0">
        <div class="container">

            <h4>BOARDER FEES STRUCTURE</h4>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        <h3 class="mb-4">All-Inclusive Boarding Fees</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-3">
                            All students at Rusumo High School are boarders paying a uniform rate of 92,000 RWF per term. This comprehensive fees include tuition, accommodation, meals, facilities access, and all educational materials.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                            Additional requirements apply when students enter a new academic level. These one-time or periodic fees cover specialized materials, uniforms, and resources specific to the new level of study.
                        </p>
                        <div class="alert alert-info border-start border-4 border-info">
                            <strong><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>Important:</strong> The 92,000 RWF per term covers all regular educational costs. Additional level-entry fees apply only when students advance to S1, S3, or S5.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg rounded-3 text-center">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <i class="fas fa-file-pdf fa-3x text-danger mb-3"></i>
                                <h5 class="card-title mb-3">View Fees Details</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-4">Access the complete fees structure document with all relevant information</p>
                                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100" href="../assets/img/fees.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                    <i class="fa fa-file-pdf-o me-2"></i> Open PDF
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pricing Tables -->
                <div class="mt-5">
                    <h3 class="mb-4 fw-bold">2025-2026 Fees Structure (Per Term - 3 Terms)</h3>
                    
                    <!-- Secondary Section (O-Level) -->
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="bg-success text-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i> Secondary Section - O-Level (S1-S4, Boarders)
                        </h4>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Item</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Per Term (RWF)</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>Total Fees (All Inclusive)</strong></td>
                                        <td class="text-center">92,000</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="table-info fw-bold">
                                        <td>TOTAL PER YEAR (3 Terms)</td>
                                        <td class="text-center">276,000</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="table-warning">
                                        <td colspan="2"><strong style="color: #856404;"><i class="fas fa-star me-2"></i>Additional Requirements for New Level Entry (S1 & S3):</strong><br/>
                                        <span style="color: #856404;">Enrollment fee, uniform kit, and learning materials package</span></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Secondary Section (A-Level) -->
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="bg-warning text-dark p-3 rounded mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-star me-2"></i> Secondary Section - A-Level (S5-S6, Boarders)
                        </h4>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Item</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Per Term (RWF)</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><strong>Total Fees (All Inclusive)</strong></td>
                                        <td class="text-center">92,000</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="table-info fw-bold">
                                        <td>TOTAL PER YEAR (3 Terms)</td>
                                        <td class="text-center">276,000</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="table-warning">
                                        <td colspan="2"><strong style="color: #856404;"><i class="fas fa-star me-2"></i>Additional Requirements for S5 Entry (New Specialization):</strong><br/>
                                        <span style="color: #856404;">Specialization materials, subject-specific lab equipment, and advanced resource package</span></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Additional Information -->
                    <div class="alert alert-light border-2 border-primary p-4 rounded">
                        <h5 class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-list me-2 text-primary"></i>Important Information</h5>
                        <ul class="mb-0">
                            <li><strong>Standard Fees:</strong> All students are boarders paying 92,000 RWF per term (3 terms per year = 276,000 RWF annually).</li>
                            <li><strong>What's Included:</strong> Tuition, accommodation, meals, library access, sports facilities, technology resources, and all standard educational materials.</li>
                            <li><strong>Additional Level Entry Fees:</strong> Special requirements apply when entering S1 (Secondary), S3 (O-Level continuation), and S5 (Advanced Level). Details available from admissions office.</li>
                            <li><strong>Payment Terms:</strong> Fees can be paid termly or annually. </li>
                            <li><strong>Payment Methods:</strong> Umwarimu SACCO Bank transfer and  mobile money (MTN, Airtel) payments through SDMS are accepted.</li>
                            <li><strong>Late Payment:</strong> Fees must be paid before term begins.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

